cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically salient object detection. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel approach that incorporates deep neural networks, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper introduces a new dataset, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
